#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:239
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/management.adoc:417
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/publishing.adoc:17
msgid "If you prefer to read, you will find the transcript below the embedded video."
msgstr "Si prefieres leer, encontrarás la transcripción debajo del vídeo incrustado."

